<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="BPAA-2056" src="/portals/14/Images/BPAA-2056.jpg?ver=2021-08-31-075129-387" style="max-width:100%; text-align:center" title="BPAA-2056" /></p>

<h2 style="text-align:center"><strong>The Call for Speakers for the 2025 International Bowl Expo&nbsp;</strong></h2>

<h2 style="text-align:center"><strong>is NOW OPEN!</strong></h2>

<p style="text-align:center"><a class="eds_btn eds_btnDanger" href="/bowlexpo/General-Info/2025-Call-for-Speakers/Application-Form" target="_blank">Application Form Here</a></p>
</div>
